    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ma_jun_734667",
        "quote": "I hope they can see that as a consumer, if they express themselves, they may make an impact and leverage their impact on the brands, and the brands can leverage their buying power on tens of thousands of polluters - suppliers - in China.",
